article_title: CompleteCare opens Vineland health clinic after delays
article_text:
F17 Complete Care Dental Assistant Eleni Paradisis, of Vineland, left, and Dental Hygienist Cookie Robinson, of Mt. Laurel, work at the newly open CompleteCare Vineland Healthcare Campus on West Sherman Avenue, Tuesday Feb. 16, 2016. The new pod layout facility consolidates the firm's Vineland locations. (Michael Ein / Staff Photographer)

F17 Complete Care CompleteCare Vineland Healthcare Campus is open on West Sherman Avenue, Tuesday Feb. 16, 2016. The new pod layout facility consolidates the firm's Vineland locations. (Michael Ein / Staff Photographer)

F17 Complete Care Heaters and fans are in use to mitigate water damage at the newly open CompleteCare Vineland Healthcare Campus on West Sherman Avenue, Tuesday Feb. 16, 2016. A sink overflowed over the weekend and flooded a section of the new medical facility. (Michael Ein / Staff Photographer)

F17 Complete Care CompleteCare Vineland Healthcare Campus is open on West Sherman Avenue, Tuesday Feb. 16, 2016. The new pod layout facility consolidates the firm's Vineland locations. (Michael Ein / Staff Photographer)

F17 Complete Care Patients meet with staff in the registration area at the newly open CompleteCare Vineland Healthcare Campus on West Sherman Avenue, Tuesday Feb. 16, 2016. The new pod layout facility consolidates the firm's Vineland locations. (Michael Ein / Staff Photographer)

F17 Complete Care Medical equipment is staged in a hallway at the newly open CompleteCare Vineland Healthcare Campus on West Sherman Avenue, Tuesday Feb. 16, 2016. The new pod layout facility consolidates the firm's Vineland locations. (Michael Ein / Staff Photographer)

F17 Complete Care President & CEO Curtis Edwards, of Bridgeton, tours an examination room at the newly open CompleteCare Vineland Healthcare Campus on West Sherman Avenue, Tuesday Feb. 16, 2016. The new pod layout facility consolidates the firm's Vineland locations. (Michael Ein / Staff Photographer)

F17 Complete Care Hedshot of President & CEO Curtis Edwards, of Bridgeton, at CompleteCare Vineland Healthcare Campus on West Sherman Avenue, Tuesday Feb. 16, 2016. The new pod layout facility consolidates the firm's Vineland locations. (Michael Ein / Staff Photographer)

F17 Complete Care CompleteCare Vineland Healthcare Campus is open on West Sherman Avenue, Tuesday Feb. 16, 2016. The new pod layout facility consolidates the firm's Vineland locations. (Michael Ein / Staff Photographer)

og.description: VINELAND — After acquiring land in a sheriff’s sale in 2013, nonprofit health-care provider CompleteCare has opened its Vineland Health Campus on Sherman Avenue.
